### MVP Graph Index

For MVP, index Markdown/MDX files into:

```text
File nodes
Section nodes
Entity/frontmatter nodes
Reference edges
Backlink edges
About/dependsOn/implements/related* edges
Path containment edges
```

Initial parser can be simple:

* Parse frontmatter.
* Split headings into sections.
* Extract known relation fields.
* Extract Markdown links.
* Extract IDs from frontmatter.

